  - Been Matchin-3's since '09
  - Gems so PHAT you can see them from the front
  - Here we are now, entertain us.
  - There's a war goin' on outside no gem is safe from
  - Now I ain't saying she a gem digger...
  - I got 99 problems, but this Match-3 aint one
  - Melts in Your Hands, Not in Your Mouth
  - Betcha You Can't Match Just One
